{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/19700", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/19700/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/19700/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/19700/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/19700", "id": 51579305, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWU1MTU3OTMwNQ==", "number": 19700, "title": "No macro hygiene for items", "user": {"login": "maxsnew", "id": 1479741, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE0Nzk3NDE=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1479741?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/maxsnew", "html_url": "https://github.com/maxsnew", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/maxsnew/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/maxsnew/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/maxsnew/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/maxsnew/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/maxsnew/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/maxsnew/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/maxsnew/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/maxsnew/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/maxsnew/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 132910982, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwxMzI5MTA5ODI=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/A-macros", "name": "A-macros", "color": "f7e101", "default": false, "description": "Area: All kinds of macros (custom derive, macro_rules!, proc macros, ..)"}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 5, "created_at": "2014-12-10T16:32:30Z", "updated_at": "2015-03-03T19:34:50Z", "closed_at": "2015-03-03T16:52:51Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "Uses of identifiers in a macro expansion refer to identifiers in the macro use-site and not the macro-definition site, effectively giving macros dynamic scope.\n\nMinimal example:\n\n``` rust\n#![feature(macro_rules)]\n\nfn foo() -> bool {\n    true\n}\n\nmacro_rules! bar(\n    () => (foo())\n)\n\n#[cfg(test)]\nmod test {\n    fn foo() -> bool {\n        false\n    }\n    #[test]\n    fn test() {\n        assert!(bar!());\n    }\n}\n```\n\nTesting this program will result in a test failure because when `bar!()` expands to `foo()` the `foo` is the `foo` in the test submodule, whereas it should refer to the `foo` in the top-level module where `bar!` was defined.\n\nThis paper is a good resource for implementing this: http://www.cs.utah.edu/plt/publications/macromod.pdf\n", "closed_by": {"login": "kmcallister", "id": 444997, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjQ0NDk5Nw==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/444997?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/kmcallister", "html_url": "https://github.com/kmcallister", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kmcallister/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kmcallister/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kmcallister/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kmcallister/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kmcallister/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kmcallister/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kmcallister/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kmcallister/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kmcallister/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/19700/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confu